        <Parent_String>fetish figures [300047498], sculpture by function [300047107], sculpture (visual works) [300047090], visual works by material or technique [300191091], visual works (works) [300191086], Visual Works (hierarchy name) [300179869], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
